All Implemented Interfaces:
EventSink<SimEvent>
public class SwfWorkloadReader extends EventFileReader
Reads a job trace in the Standard Workload Format (SWF) and creates the corresponding workload. For details on the SWF format, please check: http://www.cs.huji.ac.il/labs/parallel/workload/swf.html
Author:
Marcos Dias de Assuncao
